  "reference_number": "INU0337",
  "remarks": "\nMassoud AKHAVAN-FARD is an involved person under the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: Massoud AKHAVAN-FARD is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, promoting, or facilitating a relevant nuclear activity, namely the proliferation or development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran, or an activity that could lead to the development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran.\n",
